Revision history for URI-geo

0.01    2009-04-21
        - Initial release.

0.02    2009-04-21
        - Make new recognise objects with a location method.
        - Normalise GeoURIs at the poles.
        - Added test for Geo::Point compatibility.

0.03
        - Fix bug that meant that a call to location that updated the
          location returned the old location rather than the new one.

